# Integration-test lane flags (SCM-S49-D1). COMMITTED — contains NO secrets.
# Injected via `node --env-file=.env.test` by the `test:integration` script.
# Real Supabase credentials keep coming from .env through src/config.ts (dotenv);
# node loads this file first, dotenv then fills in the rest without overriding.
#
# Enabling this flag opts tests/budget-integration.test.ts into hitting the live
# dev Supabase. The enforcement mode (SCM_BUDGET_ENFORCEMENT_MODE) is set inside
# the test at runtime — resolveMode() in src/budget/gate.ts reads it dynamically
# per call — so it deliberately does NOT live here.
RUN_DB_TESTS=1
